        <head>Girl From Peru</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>I know this girl with flickering eyes </l>
          <l>She told me once she wants to die, </l>
          <l>But why? </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>You've got, you've got, you've got to be glad </l>
          <l>You've got, you've got, you shouldn't feel sad </l>
          <l>Don't feel guilt for haven't done. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>She's got a soul you feel from a mile </l>
          <l>And a big smile to warm my heart </l>
          <l>How could I convince that beautiful girl </l>
          <l>That there is something worth living for. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>You've got, you've got… </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>I hope those words would stay in your mind </l>
          <l>So each you hear this song you'll start to smile </l>
          <l>Forget about fucking suicide. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>You've got, you've got…</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
